---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Venba Apps" description="Privacy Policy for Venba Apps">
    <header>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="meta">Last Updated: January 10, 2025 | Version 1.0</p>
    </header>

    <section>
        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>I respect your privacy. This policy explains how I handle information in my mobile applications.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Apps Covered</h2>
        <p>This privacy policy applies to all mobile applications published by Venba Apps, including:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Privacy Expense Manager - <a href="/privacy-expense-manager">View dedicated privacy policy</a></li>
            <li>Home Loan Advisor (Coming Soon)</li>
            <li>Future applications I may publish</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 15px; padding: 15px; background: #f0f4f8; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #667eea;">
            <strong>Note:</strong> Privacy Expense Manager has its own dedicated privacy policy due to its unique privacy-first architecture and local-only data storage.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Information I Collect</h2>

        <h3>Automatically Collected</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Device Information:</strong> Device model, operating system version, unique device identifiers</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> How you interact with our apps (via Firebase Analytics)</li>
            <li><strong>Crash Reports:</strong> Information about app crashes (via Firebase Crashlytics)</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>App Data:</strong> Information you enter in the app (stored locally on your device)</li>
            <li><strong>Support Requests:</strong> Email address and messages when you contact us</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>How I Use Information</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Improve app functionality and fix bugs</li>
            <li>Understand how users interact with my apps</li>
            <li>Respond to support requests</li>
            <li>Send app-related communications (if applicable)</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
            <li>Protect against fraudulent or illegal activity</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>I do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information. I may share information only in these cases:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>With your consent:</strong> When you explicitly agree</li>
            <li><strong>Service providers:</strong> With trusted third parties who help me operate my apps (Firebase, AdMob)</li>
            <li><strong>Legal requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect rights and safety</li>
            <li><strong>Business transfers:</strong> In case of merger, acquisition, or sale of assets</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>My apps use these third-party services that may collect information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Google Firebase:</strong> Analytics, Crashlytics, Performance Monitoring
                <br><a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy">Firebase Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><strong>Google AdMob:</strong> Advertisement display (in free versions)
                <br><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy">Google Privacy Policy</a></li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Data Storage & Security</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Personal data is primarily stored locally on your device</li>
            <li>I don't store sensitive financial information on servers</li>
            <li>Analytics data is anonymized and aggregated</li>
            <li>I use industry-standard security measures</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You can:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Opt-out of analytics collection (if available in app)</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data by contacting us</li>
            <li>Disable personalized ads in your device settings</li>
            <li>Uninstall the app to remove all local data</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Data Deletion Requests</h2>
        <p>To request deletion of your data:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Email us at <a href="mailto:contact.venbaapps@gmail.com">contact.venbaapps@gmail.com</a> with subject "Data Deletion Request"</li>
            <li>Include the app name and any account identifiers (if applicable)</li>
            <li>I will process your request within 30 days</li>
            <li>Note: Some data may be retained for legal or legitimate business purposes</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Data Retention</h2>
        <p>I retain data for different periods:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Analytics Data:</strong> As per service provider policies</li>
            <li><strong>Crash Reports:</strong> As needed for debugging</li>
            <li><strong>Support Emails:</strong> As needed</li>
            <li><strong>Local App Data:</strong> Until you delete the app</li>
        </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>International Data Transfers</h2>
        <p>Your information may be transferred to and processed in countries other than your own. These countries may have different data protection laws. By using my apps, you consent to such transfers.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
        <p>My apps are not directed to children under 13. I don't knowingly collect information from children under 13.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>I may update this policy periodically. Check the "Last Updated" date above for the latest version.</p>
    </section>

    <section>
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>For privacy questions or concerns:</p>
        <p>Email: <a href="mailto:contact.venbaapps@gmail.com">contact.venbaapps@gmail.com</a></p>
    </section>

    <Footer />
</Layout>